######## Step by step guide to solve the lab. ########

1. Left Navigation menu - Storage - click Create Bucket

2. Bucket Name - {Project_ID} and click Create

3. Upload 'Sample Startup Script' 

4. Copy Public Access URL 

5. Navigation Menu - Compute Engine - VM Instances - lab monitor instance - Edit

6. Locate Metadata section

7. In the Key field, enter startup-script-url
   In the Value field, paste the URL of the remote script [Public Access URL]

8. Locate Firewall - Check HTTP

9. Save

10. Reset VM Instance - lab monitor instance

11. Click on Instance External IP - add Http://IP-ADDRESS


*Check Lab Progress*
